title: Maldives Occupancy Rate
description: Capacity Utilization in Maldives decreased to 45.20 percent in September from 59.50 percent in August of 2022. Capacity Utilization in Maldives averaged 60.98 percent from 2012 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 89.40 percent in February of 2013 and a record low of 2.50 percent in June of 2020. This page provides - Maldives Capacity Utilization - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
